{"tid":1398753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大頭仔街坊 匯報現場","createTime":"2019-08-03T02:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T02:35:26.000Z","uid":40441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"80f62e713a0edb7eba4834f4ffb4264078ce5dc6","tid":1398753,"uid":40441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:34:06.000Z","msg":"大頭仔街坊 匯報現場<br />\n晏架街公園空城中，乜都冇， <br />\n連警犬報防都冇。<br />\n建議唔好搞 晏架街 公園旁邊嘅草叢， 嗰度係出名嘅白粉位，有好多白粉針。一下唔該俾人告 藏毒就gg了<br />\n公園旁邊其實有廢鐵回收，<br />\n櫻桃街公園警犬， 出旺角嗰條橋， <strong>暫時仲未有警犬</strong>， 出旺角仲可以經 奧海城三期。<br />\n<br />\n大角咀 只係散水嘅地方唔好久留。<br />\nbe water<br />\n萬一 啲警犬發癲， 放心行入舊區， 一定會有好多街坊幫手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5eMKQDx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5eMKQDx.jpg&h=98afeaa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gTxFoYy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgTxFoYy.jpg&h=2424ca1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mrGyJYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmrGyJYA.jpg&h=c7fb125b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cRok8qh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRok8qh.jpg&h=7a15d041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HEAcRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HEAcRY.jpg&h=8afd8a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNAfXiF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNAfXiF.jpg&h=ec96cce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u9jAcR1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu9jAcR1.jpg&h=412e4911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mye4QDJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMye4QDJ.jpg&h=db2b07c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLs6jw4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: